<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>A Chungnung</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hinna lenthang kawlni a eng,
 Muikhuo thim bang zing ta puona;
 Nuoizin sau neu haibang A ngak,
 A min chu Lal Immanuel.

[V2]
 A chungnung, A chungnung,
 Chungnungpen Lal Minlun;
 Zinsau ah kumsawtin,
 Chamna tuibang luong ta hen.

[V3]
 2. A mel tui bangin tawm mahleh,
 Sietlei leh thangvana Lalpen;
 Nuoi zinmang chan do mahleu le,
 Lawibang thanga, vaihawm zing ding.

[V4]
 3. Sim leh Mala namtin vawnchawih,
 Jang semguo leh zaila'n awiin;
 &quot;Chungnungpena Lalmang Minlun,&quot;
 Ti'n Angel zai awihpih hitiu.

[V5]
 4. A dahna leh A Lalna um,
 Lei Bethlehem leh thangvanah;
 Lunggukin paibang kuoh leu hing,
 Go thildang him ngai ta puona.</lyrics>
<author>By Kamlala</author>
<hymn_number>8</hymn_number>
</song>